### Base URL Definition
@baseURL = http://localhost:3001

# --- USER AUTHENTICATION & ACCOUNT ROUTES (backend/routes/user.js) ---

### 1. Register a New User (Host)
# Note: You should update the email, name, and password for each new user you register.
POST {{baseURL}}/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Carlos Host",
    "email": "carlos.host@example.com",
    "password": "securepassword123"
}

### 2. Register a Second User (Player 2)
